cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with deep learning of image classifiers, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of intra-class variance to extend the Shannon information of SoftMax probability is a novel technique that falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper also discusses the use of the Hadamard layer, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
